## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-105">创建时不会保存的用户主体帐户。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-105">The user principal account is not persisted when it is created.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-106">若要保存帐户，请调用<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-106">To save the account, call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.Principal.Save%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-107">下面的代码示例会连接到 LDAP 域"fabrikam.com"以使用用户名和密码在中初始化<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>到"管理员"和"securelyStoredPassword。"的构造函数</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-107">The following code example connects to the LDAP domain "fabrikam.com" with the username and password initialized in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor to "administrator" and "securelyStoredPassword."</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-108">在示例中，如用户名和电子邮件地址，设置的属性在中指定的容器下创建<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>构造函数:"CN = Users，DC = fabrikam，DC = com。"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-108">The properties set in the example, such as user name and email address, are created under the container specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor: "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com."</span></span>  
  
```  
  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                         ContextType.Domain,  
                                         "fabrikam.com",   
                                         "CN=Users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",  
                                         "administrator",   
                                         "securelyStoredPassword");   
  
UserPrincipal usr = new UserPrincipal(ctx);  
  
usr.Name = "Jim Daly";  
usr.Description = "This is the user account for Jim Daly";  
usr.EmailAddress = "jimdaly@fabrikam.com";  
usr.SetPassword("securelyStoredPassword");  
usr.Save();  
  
usr.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();   
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-160">下面的代码将连接到本地计算机存储中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-160">The following code connects to the local computer store.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-161">由于在未指定凭据<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>构造函数中，使用当前线程运行的用户的凭据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-161">Since the credentials are not specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor, the credentials of the user running the current thread are used.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-162">执行搜索以查找具有 SamAccountName"来宾"的用户。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-162">A search is performed to find the user who has SamAccountName "Guest".</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-163">如果找到该用户，则将执行检查以确定是否启用此用户的帐户。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-163">If the user is found, a check is performed to determine whether this user's account is enabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0f4a6-164">如果未启用该帐户，则此代码示例将启用它。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0f4a6-164">If the account is not enabled, the example code enables it.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(ContextType.Machine);  
  
UserPrincipal usr = UserPrincipal.FindByIdentity(ctx,   
                                           IdentityType.SamAccountName,   
                                           "Guest");  
  
if(usr != null)  
{  
    if (usr.Enabled == false)  
        usr.Enabled = true;  
  
    usr.Save();  
    usr.Dispose();  
}  
ctx.Dispose();   
```
